OL,4,Ctaxes and scrap two child benefit limit
OL,6,FMPs argue that while betting companies
OL,7,Fin the UK have seen their sales grow
OL,8,Fsignificantly in recent years, they
OL,9,Femploy relatively few people, are
OL,10,Foften located outside the UK in order
OL,11,Fto minimise their tax bills, and
OL,12,Ftherefore bring "little value to the
OL,13,FUK economy".
OL,15,FThe MPs who signed the letter
OL,16,Frepresent almost half of Labour's 235
OL,17,Fbackbenchers - ramping up pressure on
OL,18,Fthe chancellor to take action.
