OL,3,C101 MPs urge Reeves to hike gambling
OL,4,Ctaxes and scrap two child benefit limit
OL,6,F Remote Gambling Duty on online
OL,7,Fslots, poker and online bingo would
OL,8,Frise from 21% to 50%.
OL,10,F Machine Games Duty on cash-prize
OL,11,Fslot machines would rise from 20% to
OL,12,F50%.
OL,14,F General Betting Duty on sports
OL,15,Fbetting, online or in betting shops,
OL,16,Fexcluding horse racing, would rise
OL,17,Ffrom 15% to 30%.
