OL,3,C101 MPs urge Reeves to hike gambling
OL,4,Ctaxes and scrap two child benefit limit
OL,6,FThe IPPR estimates these measures
OL,7,Fwould together raise an extra #3.2
OL,8,Fbillion in 2026/27 - enough to remove
OL,9,Fthe cap that only allows families to
OL,10,Fclaim benefits for their first two
OL,11,Fchildren, as well as the household
OL,12,Fbenefit cap - both introduced by
OL,13,Fprevious Conservative governments.
OL,15,FDoing so, according to the IPPR, would
OL,16,Flift 500,000 children out of poverty.
OL,18,F'It's a crazy juggle, sometimes I end
OL,19,Fup putting things on my credit card
OL,20,Fand hoping for the best', single
OL,21,Fparent Thea Jaffee told ITV News
