OL,3,C101 MPs urge Reeves to hike gambling
OL,4,Ctaxes and scrap two child benefit limit
OL,6,FThea Jaffe is a single parent with
OL,7,Fthree children under the age of
OL,8,Feleven. She works full-time but relies
OL,9,Fon state support to make ends meet
OL,11,F"I'm on #45,000 a year. I bring home,
OL,12,Fafter taxes, #2,800 a month, but the
OL,13,Fnursery fees for the (two) toddlers
OL,14,Fare #2,600 a month, so right there, we
OL,15,Falready have a problem," she told ITV
OL,16,FNews.
OL,18,FShe estimates she would be #230 a
OL,19,Fmonth better off if the two-child
OL,20,Flimit were lifted.
