OL,3,C101 MPs urge Reeves to hike gambling
OL,4,Ctaxes and scrap two child benefit limit
OL,6,F"It would make such a huge difference
OL,7,Fto day-to-day choices," she says,
OL,8,F"like being able to replace shoes when
OL,9,Fthey get worn out or being able to
OL,10,Fsend my child to a school club."
OL,12,FThe chancellor faces difficult
OL,13,Fdecisions in her Budget in November,
OL,14,Fbut many in her own party feel
OL,15,Fstrongly that increasing gambling
OL,16,Fduties to pay for scrapping policies
OL,17,Fthat contribute to child poverty
OL,18,Fshould be an easy decision to take.
