OL,3,C101 MPs urge Reeves to hike gambling
OL,4,Ctaxes and scrap two child benefit limit
OL,6,FIn April this year, the chancellor
OL,7,Fordered a consultation on simplifying
OL,8,Fthe taxation system for betting firms
OL,9,Finto a single, unified rate.
OL,11,FThe consultation has closed but has
OL,12,Fnot concluded, and it is not clear
OL,13,Fwhether the proposals would mean
OL,14,Fbetting firms see their tax bills
OL,15,Frise, fall, or remain the same.
OL,17,F'It's on the table, I launched the
OL,18,Freview', Chancellor Rachel Reeves told
OL,19,FITV News
