OL,6,FOn Monday, before the MPs' letter was
OL,7,Fsent, the chancellor told ITV News in
OL,8,Fan interview at Gatwick Airport that
OL,9,Fthe changes the IPPR and Gordon Brown
OL,10,Fare pushing for are "on the table".
OL,12,FRachel Reeves added: "I didn't need
OL,13,FMPs or former chancellors to tell me
OL,14,Fto launch an enquiry into gambling
OL,15,Ftaxation. I did that as chancellor,
OL,16,Fand I'll set out the plans on the
OL,17,Ftaxation of gambling - and indeed of
OL,18,Fother areas - in my Budget on 26
OL,19,FNovember."
