OL,6,FIn the same interview, the chancellor
OL,7,Fsaid she had already taken action to
OL,8,Freduce child poverty by rolling out
OL,9,Fmore free school meals, funding extra
OL,10,Fhours of childcare and increasing the
OL,11,Fnational minimum wage.
OL,13,FThe three biggest gambling companies
OL,14,Fin the UK are Flutter (owner of Paddy
OL,15,FPower), Entain (owner of Ladbrokes),
OL,16,Fand Bet365.
OL,18,FLast year, Denise Coates, the founder
OL,19,Fand chief executive of Bet365, took
OL,20,Fhome #158 million in pay and dividends.
