OL,6,FThe Betting and Gaming Council, which
OL,7,Frepresents the industry, says its
OL,8,Fmembers contribute #6.8 billion to the
OL,9,Feconomy, generate #4 billion in tax,
OL,10,Fand support 109,000 jobs.
OL,12,FIt has not said how these figures were
OL,13,Fcalculated.
OL,15,FThe BGC has said previously: "We
OL,16,Fcompletely reject the proposals by the
OL,17,FIPPR, which Gordon Brown has based his
OL,18,Fcalls for a drastic tax hike on, and
OL,19,Fwhich will only hit ordinary punters.
