OL,4,Ctaxes and scrap two child benefit limit
OL,6,F"These proposals are economically
OL,7,Freckless, factually misleading, and
OL,8,Frisk driving huge numbers to the
OL,9,Fgrowing, unsafe, unregulated gambling
OL,10,Fblack market, which doesn't protect
OL,11,Fconsumers and contributes zero tax."
OL,13,FThe chairman of the BGC is Michael
OL,14,FDugher, a former MP and special
OL,15,Fadviser to Gordon Brown.
