OL,3,C101 MPs urge Reeves to hike gambling
OL,4,Ctaxes and scrap two child benefit limit
OL,6,FIn a statement to ITV News, a Betting
OL,7,Fand Gaming Council spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"We strongly oppose proposals to raise
OL,9,Ftaxes on the regulated betting and
OL,10,Fgaming industry. Such a move would be
OL,11,Fshort-sighted, harming jobs,
OL,12,Finvestment, and sports funding, while
OL,13,Ffailing to deliver more revenue.
OL,15,F"BGC members already contribute #6.8
OL,16,Fbillion to the economy, pay #4 billion
OL,17,Fin taxes, and support 109,000 jobs.
OL,18,FPiling further tax rises onto the
OL,19,Fsector, on top of reforms that have
OL,20,Falready cost over #1 billion, risks
OL,21,Fundermining a responsible industry.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
