OL,6,F"Every time the Treasury squeezes the
OL,7,Fregulated sector, it strengthens the
OL,8,Funsafe black market, which pays no
OL,9,Ftax, offers no consumer protection,
OL,10,Fand puts UK jobs and growth at risk."
OL,12,FThe industry suggests higher taxes
OL,13,Fwould lead companies to offer worse
OL,14,Fodds, leading to more bets being
OL,15,Fplaced with unscrupulous operators.
OL,17,FThis argument has been challenged by
OL,18,Fcampaigners, including the co-founder
OL,19,Fof Paddy Power, Stewart Kenny.
